# Experiment 2 — Boolean and Choice Parameters

## Version 1

```groovy
pipeline {
 agent any

 parameters {
  booleanParam(name: 'RUN_TEST', defaultValue: true)
 }

 stages {

  stage('Checkout Code') {
   steps {
    git branch: 'main', url: 'https://github.com/kavyathatavarthi/exp1-cli.git'
   }
  }

  stage('Run Test') {
   when {
    expression { params.RUN_TEST == true }
