• Task 3: Create a file with BUILD_NAME as its content.
Version 4
• Task 1: Checkout repository.
• Task 2: Display Jenkins workspace path using environment variable.
• Task 3: Print all parameter values in console.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
